v3.0.0 - BREAKING CHANGES
- Library:
	- Feature: migrated from .NET Standard 2.1 to .NET 8.0.
- Unit Tests:
	- Feature: migrated from .NET Core 3.1 to .NET 8.0.
	- Feature: migrated from NUnit 3.x to NUnit 4.x. Adapted tests to the new NUnit model (Asser.AreEqual() => Assert.That()).
- Documentation:
	- Feature: updated to v3.0.0. 

v2.0.0 - BREAKING CHANGES
- Added support for sub-namespaces.
- Added XML documentation for all the methods and constructors (summaries).
- Re-organized part of the unit tests (adapted member names to the newest NW convention in ObjectMother).
- NW.MarkdownTables: .NET Standard 2.0 => 2.1.
- NW.MarkdownTables.UnitTests, NW.MarkdownTablesClient: .NET Core 2.1  => 3.1.

v1.0.0
- Initial release.